  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether providing individuals with personalized
      information on cellular aging, including telomere dynamics, will stimulate them to adhere to
      cardiac prevention strategies and improve exercise capacity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
